headline: 4 Energy Stocks to Gain Despite Oilfield Service Industry Woes
summary: Strict capital discipline by upstream energy companies is acting as a dampener, making the outlook for the Zacks Oil and Gas- Field Services industry gloomy. SLB, HAL, BKR and AROC are expected to survive the industry challenges.
